creator: BAMMS
descriptionHtml:
Propel is an application for tenants, owners, and office workers to handle expenses, guests, vendors, communities, and their daily needs. We aim to create a smarter community safer for everyone. This application also offers the opportunity for users to provide information such as merchandise, the latest news, and information around the building that helps the community.

Propel has provided features that help tenants, owners, and office workers in managing their daily lives such as Visitor Management for incoming guests, Inquiry Management for managing tenant requests, Helpdesk for providing feedback by users, Facility Booking for booking facilities, Announcement to give information provided by the property management and feeds to provide information between your neighbours.

We will continue to develop to give tranquility and satisfaction for its users and please look forward to new features in the future.
Bamms is an easy way for you to manage housing, apartment, office, or even a mall. It's time to get rid of paper work orders!!
